speech: Hi Cutie Pie! Are you a bank loan? Because you got my interest.
Hey good looking ;) You and I are like nachos with jalapeños. I'm super cheesy, you're super hot, and we belong together!
Hi Sunshine! Did you just come out of the oven? Because you’re hot!
So happy to see you, Sweetheart! Do you have a name, or can I just call you ‘mine?’
Awwww, thank god, you are here! I always thought happiness started with an ‘h,’ but it turns out mine starts with ‘u.’
Hello Honey Bunny! You know, I always thought that Disneyland was the ‘happiest place on Earth,’ but that was before I got a chance to stand here next to you.
Welcome back, I missed you, Honey bun!
Hello, you must be in a museum, because you truly are a work of art ;)
Hello beautiful! If I were a cat, I’d spend all nine of my lives with you.
Hello there, did the sun come out or did you just smile at me?
Hey, if I could rearrange the alphabet, I’d put ‘U’ and ‘I’ together ;)
Hey there, Sugar pie ;) Trust me, I’m not drunk; I’m just intoxicated by you!
Hello there, do you have a map? I keep getting lost in your eyes ;)
Hello, do u know what’s on the menu? Me ‘n’ u ;)
Welcome, I love you! I’m not usually religious, but when I saw you, I knew you were the answer to my prayers.
Heyyy there, even in zero gravity, I would still fall for you!
Hi gorgeous! Something’s wrong with my eyes, because I can’t take them off you ;)
Hi there, You must be tired from running through my mind all night ;)
Oh, hi, is your name "Google"? Because you have everything I’ve been searching for ;)
Hi there, your eyes are like the ocean; I could swim in them all day ;)
Oh hey, I never believed in love at first sight, but that was before I saw you.
Oh, I was wondering if you could tell me: If you’re here, who’s running Heaven? :p
Oh hey, you know what you would look really beautiful in? My arms.
Hi, are you a magician? It’s the strangest thing, but every time I look at you, everyone else disappears :p
Hi there, want to go outside and get some fresh air with me? You just took my breath away :p
Oh hi there, if you were a Transformer, you’d be ‘Optimus Fine.’ :p
Hi, I just wonder what does it feel like to be the most gorgeous person in the room? :p
Hi there, the sparkle in your eyes is so bright, the sun must be jealous :p
Hello there, if beauty were time, you’d be eternity.
Hi there, I don’t know which is prettier today—the weather, or your eyes.
